	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is it possible to get GRADIUS II to work with POWERPAK?
<br />
<br />After I did the FDS sound mod &amp; replaced some mappers with LOOPYS mappers, FDS sound, &amp; Akumajo Densetsu now works!
<br />
<br />But is there a way to make Gradius II to work?
<br />I love both the NES version, and the PC-engine version.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
