	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Depends on the ROM you have, I suppose.  I've seen two versions of this game floating around -- a hacked-up MMC3 (I think) version, and the (proper/original) VRC4 version.
<br />
<br />If the PowerPak has support for the Konami VRC4, then the proper/original ROM should work fine.  If not, best get in contact with whoever maintains the PowerPak firmware code and ask them to add VRC4 support.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

